{"tid":1558045,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全民公投集會確認中共違反中英聯合聲明？","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T00:50:14.000Z","uid":270871,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5144b8a15bcdc520e732c9c3b254fcab0f573897","tid":1558045,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:30:31.000Z","msg":"中英聯合聲明有幾重要相信大家都知<br />\n外國例如G7係唔會同你講咩基本法，而係講中英聯合聲明<br />\n我哋人權嘅保障係基於呢份國際聲明，而唔係中共可以任意解讀嘅基本法<br />\n呢份嘢先係中共管治合法性嘅依據<br />\n<br />\n咁點樣搞呢？<br />\n<strong><ins>1. 用腳投票，大遊行抗議中共違反中英聯合聲明</ins></strong><br />\n缺點：冇選項冇真公投feel<br />\n實際人數會有爭議<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2. 搞個集會真係一人一票公投</ins></strong><br />\n優點：展示公眾嘅決策能力，<span style=\"color: red;\">為將來做更多民間決策鋪路</span><br />\n搞得成嘅話絕對係個奇蹟<br />\n<br />\n缺點：確認身份有困難，為保參加者安全，應該唔可以真係確認身份證，所以好難避免有人重複投票<br />\n<br />\n民間公投技術上應該會有好多挑戰<br />\n但係如果搞得成，絕對會係震撼國際嘅歷史性一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503345a6eb69ee1162b98d859971473d7a6a3757","tid":1558045,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da5dd1a50a90e2edc6181da35b7b7ceaa9978ee","tid":1558045,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6a9609bdc8fb5d94795ae4459b7c4f8d029426","tid":1558045,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"503345a6eb69ee1162b98d859971473d7a6a3757","tid":1558045,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:32:39.00